content: Express32S features do not support auto-negotiation to a data link rate of 2 or 4 Gbps (only 8, 16, or 32 Gbps) for point-to-point connections. A compatible switch must be used to connect to lower speed devices. Consideration: FICON Express16SA features do not support auto-negotiation to a data link rate of 2 or 4 Gbps (only 8 or 16 Gbps) for point-to-point connections. A compatible switch must be used to connect to lower speed devices. Chapter 4.
